{
  "stem": "3757.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She went-- she took a-- occasional jobs to be always around us if it is something happens to us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And she came sometimes to-- to visit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I told him, Irene, don't come, because we don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It can happen that they will take us away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "If you are here, they will take you, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And she said, if they take you, I go where you go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It's-- it reminded me to Ruth's story from the Bible.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And she did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "She-- she really was that way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the meantime, I took a Jewish girl because I still-- with the yellow star, I went to my business.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this went on to-- to-- in the-- in the end of August or the mid-August, started to be a little milder, not-- not so strict against the Jews.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By-- by the meantime, they took away all the Jews from the country.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Were no Jews anymore in the country but in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they-- I showed to you that one was a Rosh Hashanah and Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they permitted that we go out at the evening to go to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Otherwise, we were permitted only from 11:00 to 5 o'clock to be out of the house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we could go shopping only between 12:00 and 1:00.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I was not home that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I-- [LAUGHS] I sent my little son before that, who was 2 years old and had not to get the yellow star.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He went shopping.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And he was so cute.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Once, a grocer was at-- at-- at-- not a grocery store.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Such a fruit store.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I told him, buy me two, three tomatoes and two green peppers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I saw that he goes in and look the-- the tomatoes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he bought the.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
